- Standard rate for shipping is considered to be $5.00 or less; anything above is considered pricier;
- "Gmail users" are customers whose email addresses end with '@gmail.com';
- The number of orders represents the number of purchases made by each customer from each supplier.

- "gardeners" refers to customers;
- "bountiful harvests" correspond to the total amount of money spent;
- "seeds sown" symbolizes the orders placed by the customers.

sql:
SELECT product_name, price
FROM products
WHERE product_id < 10;
